00045 void CHPMultiDataFileWriterTest::WriteTestGeno()
00046 {
00047         ParameterNameValueTypeList params;
00048         ParameterNameValueType param;
00049 
00050         CHPMultiDataData data("CHP_MultiData_file");
00051 
00052         data.SetAlgName(L"sig");
00053         data.SetAlgVersion(L"1.0");
00054         data.SetArrayType(L"test3");
00055         data.SetEntryCount(GenotypeMultiDataType, 2, 10);
00056 
00057         param.SetName(L"an1");
00058         param.SetValueText(L"av1");
00059         params.push_back(param);
00060         data.AddAlgParams(params);
00061 
00062         params.clear();
00063         param.SetName(L"sn1");
00064         param.SetValueText(L"sv1");
00065         params.push_back(param);
00066         data.AddSummaryParams(params);
00067 
00068 
00069         CHPMultiDataFileWriter *writer = new CHPMultiDataFileWriter(data);
00070         affymetrix_calvin_data::ProbeSetMultiDataGenotypeData e;
00071 
00072         writer->SeekToDataSet(GenotypeMultiDataType);
00073         e.name = "abc";
00074         e.confidence = 10.0f;
00075         writer->WriteEntry(e);
00076         e.name = "xyz";
00077         e.confidence = 20.0f;
00078         writer->WriteEntry(e);
00079 
00080         delete writer;
00081 
00082         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(1);
00083 
00085 
00086         CHPMultiDataData data2;
00087         CHPMultiDataFileReader reader;
00088         reader.SetFilename("CHP_MultiData_file");
00089         reader.Read(data2);
00090 
00091         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(data2.GetAlgName() == L"sig");
00092         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(data2.GetAlgVersion() == L"1.0");
00093         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(data2.GetArrayType() == L"test3");
00094         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(data2.GetEntryCount(GenotypeMultiDataType) == 2);
00095         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(data2.GetEntryCount(ExpressionMultiDataType) == 0);
00096 
00097         ParameterNameValueTypeList p = data2.GetAlgParams();
00098         ParameterNameValueTypeList::iterator it = p.begin();
00099         param = *it;
00100         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(param.GetName() == L"an1");
00101         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(param.GetValueText() == L"av1");
00102 
00103         p = data2.GetSummaryParams();
00104         it = p.begin();
00105         param = *it;
00106         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(param.GetName() == L"sn1");
00107         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(param.GetValueText() == L"sv1");
00108 
00109 
00110     data2.GetGenotypeEntry(GenotypeMultiDataType, 0, e);
00111         CPPUNIT_ASSERT_DOUBLES_EQUAL(e.confidence, 10.0f, 0.0001f);
00112         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(e.name == "abc");
00113         data2.GetGenotypeEntry(GenotypeMultiDataType, 1, e);

00115         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(e.name == "xyz");

00279 {
00280         ParameterNameValueTypeList params;
00281         ParameterNameValueType param;
00282 
00283         CHPMultiDataData data("CHP_MultiData_file");
00284 
00285     vector<ColumnInfo> cols;
00286     IntColumn icol(L"int");

00289     cols.push_back(fcol);
00290 
00291         data.SetAlgName(L"sig");
00292         data.SetAlgVersion(L"1.0");
00293         data.SetArrayType(L"test3");
00294         data.SetEntryCount(ExpressionMultiDataType, 1, 10);
00295         data.SetEntryCount(GenotypeMultiDataType, 2, 10, cols);
00296 
00297         CHPMultiDataFileWriter *writer = new CHPMultiDataFileWriter(data);
00298         affymetrix_calvin_data::ProbeSetMultiDataExpressionData ex;
00299     affymetrix_calvin_data::ProbeSetMultiDataGenotypeData gn;
00300 
00301     // expression
00302         writer->SeekToDataSet(ExpressionMultiDataType);
00303         ex.name = "ex1";
00304     ex.quantification = 10.0f;
00305         writer->WriteEntry(ex);
00306 
00307     // genotype
00308     writer->SeekToDataSet(GenotypeMultiDataType);
00309         gn.name = "gn1";
00310         gn.call = 1;
00311     gn.confidence = 11.0f;
00312     gn.metrics.clear();
00313     param.SetValueInt32(1);
00314     gn.metrics.push_back(param);
00315     param.SetValueFloat(2.0f);
00316     gn.metrics.push_back(param);
00317         writer->WriteEntry(gn);
00318 
00319         gn.name = "gn2";
00320         gn.call = 2;
00321     gn.confidence = 22.0f;;
00322     gn.metrics.clear();
00323     param.SetValueInt32(2);
00324     gn.metrics.push_back(param);
00325     param.SetValueFloat(3.0f);
00326     gn.metrics.push_back(param);
00327         writer->WriteEntry(gn);
00328 
00329         delete writer;
00330 
00331         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(1);
00332 
00334 
00335         CHPMultiDataData data2;
00336         CHPMultiDataFileReader reader;
00337         reader.SetFilename("CHP_MultiData_file");
00338         reader.Read(data2);
00339 
00340         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(data2.GetAlgName() == L"sig");
00341         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(data2.GetAlgVersion() == L"1.0");
00342         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(data2.GetArrayType() == L"test3");
00343         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(data2.GetEntryCount(ExpressionMultiDataType) == 1);
00344         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(data2.GetEntryCount(GenotypeMultiDataType) == 2);
00345 
00346     // expression
00347     CPPUNIT_ASSERT(data2.GetNumMetricColumns(ExpressionMultiDataType) == 0);
00348     data2.GetExpressionEntry(ExpressionMultiDataType, 0, ex);
00349         CPPUNIT_ASSERT_DOUBLES_EQUAL(ex.quantification, 10.0f, 0.0001f);
00350         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(ex.name == "ex1");
00351 
00352     // genotype
00353     CPPUNIT_ASSERT(data2.GetNumMetricColumns(GenotypeMultiDataType) == 2);
00354     CPPUNIT_ASSERT(data2.GetMetricColumnName(GenotypeMultiDataType, 0) == L"int");
00355     CPPUNIT_ASSERT(data2.GetMetricColumnName(GenotypeMultiDataType, 1) == L"float");
00356 
00357     data2.GetGenotypeEntry(GenotypeMultiDataType, 0, gn);
00358         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(gn.call == 1);
00359         CPPUNIT_ASSERT_DOUBLES_EQUAL(gn.confidence, 11.0f, 0.0001f);
00360         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(gn.name == "gn1");
00361     CPPUNIT_ASSERT(gn.metrics.size() == 2);
00362     param = gn.metrics[0];

00364     CPPUNIT_ASSERT(param.GetValueInt32() == 1);
00365     param = gn.metrics[1];
00366     CPPUNIT_ASSERT(param.GetParameterType() == ParameterNameValueType::FloatType);
00367     CPPUNIT_ASSERT_DOUBLES_EQUAL(param.GetValueFloat(), 2.0f, 0.00001f);
00368 
00369     data2.GetGenotypeEntry(GenotypeMultiDataType, 1, gn);
00370         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(gn.call == 2);
00371         CPPUNIT_ASSERT_DOUBLES_EQUAL(gn.confidence, 22.0f, 0.0001f);
00372         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(gn.name == "gn2");
00373     CPPUNIT_ASSERT(gn.metrics.size() == 2);
00374     param = gn.metrics[0];
00375     CPPUNIT_ASSERT(param.GetParameterType() == ParameterNameValueType::Int32Type);
00376     CPPUNIT_ASSERT(param.GetValueInt32() == 2);
00377     param = gn.metrics[1];

00379     CPPUNIT_ASSERT_DOUBLES_EQUAL(param.GetValueFloat(), 3.0f, 0.00001f);
